'''柯纳德·韦恩·里嘉摩拉'''（{{lang-en|Conrad Wayne Ricamora}}；{{bd|1979年|2月17日}}）是一个美国演员与歌手，最为人所知的是在[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]电视剧《[[逍遙法外_(電視劇)|逍遥法外]]》中扮演的角色奥利弗·汉普顿。 

== 职业生涯 ==
柯纳德在2013年外百老汇的音乐剧《[[爱在这里|爱在这里]]》（''Here Lies Love''）中扮演尼诺·阿基诺,赢得了一个[[世界剧院奖|世界剧院奖]]和[[露西尔罗特奖|露西尔罗特奖]]的音乐剧最佳男演员的提名。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Theatre World Awards - Theatre World Awards|url=http://www.theatreworldawards.org/past-recipients.html|access-date=2021-11-01|work=www.theatreworldawards.org|archive-date=2018-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012122808/http://www.theatreworldawards.org/past-recipients.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Lortel Archives|url=http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=people&first=Conrad&last=Ricamora&middle=|accessdate=2015-09-27|publisher=The Internet Off-Broadway Database|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007165024/http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=people&first=Conrad&last=Ricamora&middle=|archivedate=2015-10-07|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

在2014年他扮演了《[[捉智雙雄|逍遥法外]]》的奥利弗·汉普顿，[[傑克·法洛希|杰克·法洛希]]剧中的情人。<ref>{{Cite web|title="How To Get Away With Murder" Actor Jack Falahee: Connor is a "Creature Of Appetites"|url=http://www.thebacklot.com/how-to-get-away-with-murder-jack-falahee-on-connor-as-a-creature-of-appetites/10/2014/|accessdate=28 October 2014|work=thebacklot.com|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905124106/http://www.thebacklot.com/how-to-get-away-with-murder-jack-falahee-on-connor-as-a-creature-of-appetites/10/2014/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=On the Town: Summer Fridays at 'Here Lies Love'|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/suzy-evans/on-the-town-summer-friday_b_5698619.html|accessdate=28 October 2014|date=22 August 2014|work=The Huffington Post|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304072634/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/suzy-evans/on-the-town-summer-friday_b_5698619.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也继续在第二季中客串。 在第二季终集播放一天之后，2016年3月18日，里嘉摩拉在接下来的第三季被提升为正规的演员。<ref>{{Cite web|title=HTGAWM Promotes Conrad Ricamora to Series Regular in Season 3|url=http://tvline.com/2016/03/18/how-to-get-away-with-murder-season-3-conrad-ricamora-series-regular-oliver/|access-date=2016-03-18|website=TVLine|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319211828/http://tvline.com/2016/03/18/how-to-get-away-with-murder-season-3-conrad-ricamora-series-regular-oliver/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2015年[[林肯中心剧院|林肯中心剧院]]百老汇复兴戏剧，[[罗杰斯与哈默斯坦|罗杰斯与哈默斯坦]]的[[國王與我|国王与我]]，扮演伦萨。<ref name="Brantley2015">Brantley, Ben. </ref>这部戏剧卡司录制的原声带获得了[[葛萊美獎|格莱美奖]]最佳戏剧专辑提名。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Grammy Nominations 2016 Full List|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/grammy-nominations-2016-full-list-846297|accessdate=2015-12-16|website=The Hollywood Reporter|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308072435/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/grammy-nominations-2016-full-list-846297|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
里嘉摩拉出生在美国加州的圣塔玛利亚，父亲是罗恩·里嘉摩拉，曾在美国空军服役；母亲是黛比·伯伦德，一个社会工作者。他的父亲出生于菲律宾马尼拉，10岁时移民美国。 普遍认为他父亲具有菲律宾血统，但是他是被收养的。母亲则有德国与爱尔兰血统.<ref name="out">{{Cite web|title=Jose Llana & Conrad Ricamora, stars of Here Lies Love, on their personal journeys of self-acceptance|url=http://www.out.com/entertainment/theater-dance/2014/07/30/here-lies-love-stars-jose-llana-conrad-ricamora-filipino-marcos-musical|accessdate=28 October 2014|work=Out Magazine|archive-date=2019-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331192823/https://www.out.com/entertainment/theater-dance/2014/07/30/here-lies-love-stars-jose-llana-conrad-ricamora-filipino-marcos-musical|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="fans">{{Cite web|title=Conrad Ricamora Fans|url=http://conradricamorafans.tumblr.com/trivia|accessdate=2015-11-06|website=conradricamorafans.tumblr.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304101748/http://conradricamorafans.tumblr.com/trivia|archivedate=2016-03-04|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

